title: Painted Lion Holiday Magnet
description:
Magnet of an oil painting that features the front of the museum and Edward Kemeys’ Lions, 1893, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

A magnet of an oil painting of the front of the museum featuring  Edward Kemeys’ Lions, 1893, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.  In this image the Lions are wreathed for the winter holidays.

  • Single Magnet. 
  • Dimensions: 3.625 x 2.5 in.
